    "text": "Yes, you were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "Now, in conclusion, my administration will focus on the three R's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "Reading, writing, and refilling the ocean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "As you know, we've inherited quite a budget crunch from President Trump."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "How bad is it, Secretary Van Houten?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "We're broke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "The country is broke?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "How can that be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "Well, remember when the last administration decided to invest in our nation's children?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Big mistake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "The balanced breakfast program just created a generation of ultra-strong super criminals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "And midnight basketball taught them to function without sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "What about my pledge to build the world's largest bookmobile?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "Isn't there any money left for that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "And we borrowed from every country in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Quick, Lisa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "Call off your..."
